{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Prohibit police officers guilty of serious crimes from receiving their pension",
        "additional_details": "I am the victim of a police officer-perpetrated crime \u2013 the officer was sentenced to eight years in prison and after being found guilty and whilst awaiting sentencing, was still being paid a wage and pension.",
        "background": "We urge the Government to legislate to stop police officers convicted of serious crimes from receiving their police, public-funded pensions.",
